{
  "id": "adv_main_04_04_01",
  "title": "星空編1章16話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n星見プロ主催でフェスをするって本当なんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nIs it true that Hoshimi Prods. is hosting a festival!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2775448712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まだ正式に決まった訳じゃないが\n開催する方向で話を進めているところだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not officially decided yet‚\nbut we're in discussions toward holding it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "それは素晴らしいですわね！\n私達が主役なら華やかなイベントになりますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds fantastic!\nWe are the main characters‚ it'll be a spectacular event!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "フェスではライブの他に\n星見プロにまつわる企画を行うと聞きましたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard that in addition to live performances‚\nthe festival will also feature Hoshimi Productions-related projects…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、会場に来たファンが一日中楽しめる\nお祭りにしたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ I want to make it a festival that fans who come to the venue\ncan enjoy all day long",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.700001653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "お祭りかあ……すっごく楽しそうだね！\n企画ってどんなことをするの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A festival… that sounds so much fun!\nWhat are you planning to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.300001653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そこは、みんなから案を募りたいと思っている\n今回のフェスは星見プロのみんなで作り上げるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'm thinking of gathering everyone's opinions\nThis festival is made by all of Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4333349864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 50.200001653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私達が一から作り上げるイベント……\n大変そうですが、やりがいがありますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An event we're building from the ground up…\nIt seems difficult‚ but it looks rewarding!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3666683197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの他にもステージで何かやりたいな\nトークショーとか、バラエティ企画とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides live performances‚ I'd like to do something on stage\nMaybe a talk show or a variety show",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3333375295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "グッズを作るのもいいかもしれません\n私達のオリジナルグッズを考えるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe making goods would be good\nI'm thinking about our own original goods",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0000041962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はファンのみんなと交流したいな～\n握手会とか、みんなでゲームをするとか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei wants to interact with all my fans~\nA handshake event or playing games together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4333375295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "夢が広がるわね。星見プロのアイドルが集結する\n一大イベント……どんな内容になるのか楽しみだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My dreams are expanding. A grand event gathering together\nHoshimi Production idols… I can't wait to see what it'll be like",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7369653489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのアイドルが集結……\nそう考えると、リズノワがいないのは残念ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the idols from Hoshimi Prods. will be gathering together…\nNow that I think about it‚ it's a shame LizNoir won't be there",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0000041962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワはアメリカに滞在中ですからね\nフェスまでに帰国出来るといいのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir is in the America\nI hope they can return home in time for the festival…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1333375295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そうか、みんなにはまだ伝わっていなかったか\nリズノワなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Oh‚ everyone hasn't heard about it yet\nLizNoir is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.000001653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6267136574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.7
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 107.8267136574
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.8267136574
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.6933793069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "とうちゃ～く！　ついに帰って来ましたよ、日本！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Arrived~! We're finally back‚ it's Japan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6933793069,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 739.9546623000077,
          "startTime": 110.4333339692
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.2190936884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "日本に帰って来ると落ち着きますね\nはぁ……懐かしい日本の匂いです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel relieved to be back in Japan.\nHaa… it’s the smell of Japan that I miss",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2333339692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.8257376831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "まだ空港に着いただけでしょ\n落ち着くのは気が早いわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've only just arrived at the airport\nIt's too early to feel relieved",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6000006359,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 140.92961939999782,
          "startTime": 123.9666673025
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.1354653519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、出迎えが誰もいないなんておかしくないですか？\nBIG4のリズノワが帰国したんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ isn't it strange that no one welcomes us?\nLizNoir of the BIG4 has returned to Japan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7666673025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.3386628629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "空港では沢山のファンがこころ達を出迎えて\n大勢の報道陣に囲まれるのがあるべき姿じゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shouldn't Kokoro and the others be welcomed by countless fans and\nsurrounded by reporters at the airport?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7861408394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.5954881193
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "僕らの帰国は突然決まったから\nファンのみんなも知らないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our return was decided suddenly‚\nso even our fans didn't know",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.2666656495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "どこにも情報を出していないのに\n出迎えが大勢いたら、情報漏洩で逆に怖いわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We didn't announce it anywhere\nIf many people come to welcome us‚ I'm afraid of information leaks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0666673025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.0582543851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに告知はしてませんけど……大人気アイドルの\nこころ達に誰も気付かないなんて納得いきません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that we didn't announce it… no one noticed\nKokoro and the others‚ who are hugely popular idols… I can't accept it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.2333339692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.2782539846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "もっと「こころちゃん可愛い」「こころちゃん大好き」\nって歓声があってしかるべきだと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should be more cheers of 'Kokoro-chan is so cute'\nand 'I love Kokoro-chan'!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.4000006359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
